Title: Enacts the interstate medical licensure compact and the nurse licensure compact
Summary: Enacts the interstate medical licensure compact and the nurse licensure compact to strengthen access to health care by providing a streamlined process to become licensed in multiple states.
LawCode: Add Art 169 §§8860 - 8884, ren Art 170 to be Art 171, add Title 8 Art 170 §§8900 - 8911, Ed L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to enacting the interstate medical licensure compact and the nurse licensure compact
